votebox.middle.view.widget

Class NavigationLinks

  • java.lang.Object
    • votebox.middle.view.widget.NavigationLinks

  • public class NavigationLinks
extends java.lang.Object
    This class encapsulates the links that a focusable uses to determine who gets the focus when it is pushed away from a focusable in any given direction.
